  "texts": [
    "LLMs have been pivotal in various web-related tasks such as HTML understanding [24], information extraction [33], and web page summarization [16].",
    "Language models specific to HTML like HTLM [6], Webformer [23], DOM-LM [19], and MarkupLM [31] have been developed.",
    "Their integration into software testing has been innovative [27,30,36,42,44,51].",
    "Mind2Web introduces a dataset with real-world web applications using LLMs, but its understanding of form semantics is limited [18].",
    "In contrast, FormNexus leverages FERG to enrich web form semantics, enhancing form filling effectiveness."
  ],
